Edition:
Quote:  (Central Otago) On Saturday we went over into the other gully and watched a man ground-sluicing. Saw him wash out 2 dishes of dirt. He showed us his morning's work, about 1-1/2 oz. and grumbled at that [sic] I wish he had given us the claim.
